<script>
  (function () {
  try {
      var callback = function () {

          if (targetElem) {
              var headings = document.getElementsByClassName("notification-alert-wrapper__heading");
              var infoNotes;
              var wrapperElement;
              if (headings && headings.length){
                  //Find the COVID banner
                  for (var i = 0; i < headings.length; i++){
                      if (headings[i].innerText.indexOf("Unlimited Free Delivery with FreshPass") != -1 ){
                          parentElement = headings[i].parentElement;
                          wrapperElement = parentElement.closest(".notification-alert-wrapper");

                          //Replace Heading Text
                          headings[i].innerText = "Alcohol Availability Update";
                          headings[i].classList.add("target-updated-heading");

                          //Get info-notes
                          infoNotes = parentElement.getElementsByClassName("notification-alert-wrapper__info-note");

                          //Replace info-note text
                          if (infoNotes && infoNotes.length){
                              for (var j = 0; j < infoNotes.length; j++){
                                  infoNotes[j].innerText = "On Sundays, spirits are only available for delivery/pickup after 11am.";
                                  infoNotes[j].classList.add("target-updated-note");
                              }
                          }

                          //Get all svg tags
                          svgs = targetElem.getElementsByTagName('svg');
                          //Change the color of the "next" caret icon 
                          if (svgs && svgs.length){
                              for (var j = 0; j < svgs.length; j++){
                                  svgs[j].childNodes[1].childNodes[1].setAttribute("fill", "#FFFFFF");
                              }
                          }
                          
                          //Change the color of the close button "X"
                          if (wrapperElement){
                            var closeButton = wrapperElement.getElementsByClassName("notification-alert-wrapper__close-button");
                            if (closeButton && closeButton.length){
                                closeButton = closeButton[0];
                                var closeButtonSVGElems = closeButton.getElementsByTagName("g");

                                    }
                                }
                            }

                            //Change bg color of this slide
                            wrapperElement.classList.add("target-updated-slide");
                          }
                      }
                  }
              }
              
              
              targetElem.classList.add("eot-1494-added-by-Target");
